            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社20日專訊》小米(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01810-HK</a>)於11:52am錄得1手153萬股非自動對盤,每股造58元,較上日收市價低0.3%,涉資8874萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　小米現價跌0.6%,報57.85元;成交1.63億股,成交金額93.41億元,主動買沽比率48:52,資金淨主動賣出3.44億元。(rw)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
